= MODULE

augeas 

= DESCRIPTION

This is the augeas module.
Configure and manage augeas

See http://projects.puppetlabs.com/projects/puppet/wiki/Puppet_Augeas

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

== Main classes

* augeas($version) :: Install and configure augeas

== Sample Usage

     include augeas
     
